reviewText: Ordered this to add to my wonderful Billy Boyd collection! :)
This was a bit off.  I like odd stories; but not such a great ending to the plot.  Not a dvd I will keep in my collection to watch again or share.
I love the story and the music is great.  I watched it a second time and found even more interesting things in it.  It is a very clever, well acted movie.
This is a fascinating story and Billy Boyd is of course incredible in it, he is incredible in EVERYTHING thing he does, I hope Amazon will offer other hard to find movies of Billy's soon
